title: BRIEF-TrustBuddy expects to have sufficient funds to reach break-even in 2016
text:
Sept 14 TrustBuddy AB :
* Says is expected to have sufficient funds to reach break-even in 2016, if proposed capital raise to be voted on during Sept. 18, 2015 extraordinary general meeting is successful
